Package: simpleECS
Title: Communicating with Amazon Web Services(AWS) Elastic Container Service(ECS) using AWS REST APIs
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jiefei",
           family = "Wang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "szwjf08@gmail.com")
Description: 
    The package provides the most basic commands for communicating 
    with AWS ECS. The functions will have the prefix `ecs_` or
    `ec2_` depending on the class of the API. The request will be sent via the REST 
    APIs and the parameter is given by an R list object. See `?AWS_APIs` for the details.
